{"id":"428835640537739_439714512783185","type":"status","created_time":"2013-03-28T19:58:21+0000","message":"ami Parvez, Dubai Vai ami UAE te thaki. Prai 15 lakh Bangladeshi kaj kore ei deshe, jar beshir vag sadharon sromik. Tara j ki poriman koste ache ta nijer chokhe na dekhle bissas kora jai na. Kew ache mash seshe ja beton pai tate nijer khawar khoroch cholena abar barite ki pathabe. Onekei bolechen bhai jokhon Bangladesh ambussy te jai Potaka dekhlei buk vore jai. Kintu jokhon nijer somossar somadhan na peye firee ashi tokhon chorom ghrina neye ber hoye ashi. Maje moddhe vabi Muktijuddhara ki vul korechen desh sadhin kore ? R desh theke jokhon kamla bola hoy tokhon sorkar kono bebosthai nilona. Ha bhai amra kamla tai dami dami garite chore beran, upovog koren aram ayesh. R ki bolbo ? Deshe Alem somajer proti j ottachar kora hocche tate mone hoy deshe muslim thakte dibena. Jiboner prothom vote awamileague k deye j vul korechi ta abar korte chaina. Ekhon ami bidesh theke Jamaat a Islamir pokkhe prochar chalacchi. Ami mone kori eta amar Imani daitto. Qur-an houk Bangladesher songbidhan ei kamona roylo. Joy houk Din Islamer. Allah hafez."}